- Or tie.

39:24.738 --> 39:26.364
Well, we don't tie.

39:26.448 --> 39:28.241
Yeah, fuck ties.

39:28.325 --> 39:31.870
[laughs] No, but seriously,
you made us both

39:31.953 --> 39:33.955
the best versions of ourselves.

