44:35.465 --> 44:37.008
It's been hard.

44:37.092 --> 44:38.676
You know?

44:41.638 --> 44:43.264
Today was good.

44:45.308 --> 44:48.520
♪ She can't tell
the difference yet...

44:48.603 --> 44:50.271
Okay, look,
not that I want you two

44:50.355 --> 44:53.942
