45:00.865 --> 45:02.742
Belly, earlier.

45:02.826 --> 45:05.578
♪ That's what you're
coming for and...

45:05.662 --> 45:07.455
[laughs] What?

45:07.539 --> 45:09.791
♪ You drop your bag
to the floor and...

45:09.874 --> 45:12.043
It's just an observation, man.

45:13.753 --> 45:16.756
- I appreciate your observation.
- [laughs] Yeah.

