- Oh, thank you.

45:43.575 --> 45:46.703
- Do you have a name yet?
- Her name is Mildred.

45:46.786 --> 45:48.997
Mildred. I like it.

45:49.080 --> 45:51.249
How come you didn't
want another Junior Mint?

45:51.332 --> 45:54.043
I'm not 13 years old
anymore, Conrad.

45:54.127 --> 45:55.837
[♪ Angel Olsen: "Go Home"]

45:55.920 --> 45:57.922
